high_descs: Move to stand at the counter space to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter that's closest to the fridge.
Turn left to face the loaf of bread on the counter.
Place the knife on the gray plate to the right of the bread.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it from the counter.
Turn around, move past the fridge, and then turn left to get positioned between the fridge and table, facing the table.
Place the plate and knife on the table in the center of the butter knife and two heads of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate with a knife on it to the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn left, take a right at the sink and walk to the counter ahead.
Pick up the knife from the far right corner of the counter.
Turn left to face the loaf of bread on the counter.
Put the knife on the black plate to the right of the loaf of bread on the counter.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the wooden round table ahead.
Put the plate with the knife in between the heads of lettuce in the middle of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a knife on a table.

high_descs: Step forward to face the counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and step forward to face the corner of the counter.
Place the knife in the plate on the back of the counter.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it.
Turn around and walk across the room and face the kitchen table.
Place the plate with a knife on it on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife on a plate as well as place them on the kitchen table.
